				<time class="comment-time" datetime="2015-11-19T09:05:58+00:00" itemprop="commentTime"><a href="http://sweetlittlekitchen.com/mexican-chocolate-atole/#comment-2521" class="comment-time-link" itemprop="url">November 19, 2015 at 9:05 am</a></time>			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="comment-content" itemprop="commentText">
			
			<p>Thanks Jenna! Hope your family enjoys it a ton <img src="http://sweetlittlekitchen.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/simple-smile.png" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p>
